# Course Structure: Compiler Construction

## Materials Index

| # | Filename | Title | Type | Status |
|---|----------|-------|------|--------|
| 1 | lexical-analysis-lecture-notes.md | Lexical Analysis — Lecture Notes (Dr. Bennett & Dr. Omaegbu) | text/lecture notes | ✓ Processed |

